{"article_id":"bHaUT0CJRWpAsHHO","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Trying to jump-start his second-term agenda ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"President Obama called on House lawmakers Thursday to approve comprehensive immigration reform ,","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"saying","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"that current system \" isn ' t fair . \"","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"\" We have kicked this particular can down the road for too long , \"","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Mr. Obama said with supporters of immigration reform in the East Room of the White House .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"\" This is the moment","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"when we should be able to finally get the job done .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Let ' s go get it done . \"","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"House Republican leaders said Wednesday","depth":3},{"id":10,"text":"they still intend to hold an immigration debate this year ,","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"but they won ' t take up the kind of comprehensive reform plan","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"approved by the Senate .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"After a 16-day government shutdown , the legislative calendar is short for Mr. Obama to get his priorities acted on this year .","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"The president said","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"the Senate bill ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"which grants a pathway to citizenship for an estimated 11 million illegal immigrants ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"would be good for the economy and for the country .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Republican leaders should disregard the politics of the issue .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"\" I ' m not running for office again ;","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"I just believe","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"this is the right thing","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"to do , \"","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"Mr. Obama said .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"\" What we can ' t do is just sweep the problem under the rug one more time .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Let ' s not delay ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"and let ' s do it in a bipartisan fashion . \"","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"\" It ' s not smart .","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"It ' s not fair .","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"It doesn ' t make sense , \"","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"Mr. Obama said .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"Speaker John A. Boehner , Ohio Republican , said through a spokesman","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"that the president isn ' t going to get his wish .","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"\" The speaker agrees","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"that America has a broken immigration system","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"and we need reform","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"that would boost our economy , \"","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"said spokesman Brendan Buck .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"\" He ' s also been clear","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"that the House will not consider any massive , Obamacare-style legislation","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"that no one understands .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Instead , the House is committed to a common sense , step-by-step approach","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"that gives Americans confidence","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"that reform is done the right way .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"We hope","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"that the president will work with us","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"- not against us -","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"as we pursue this deliberate approach . \"","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":97,"left":57,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":57,"left":52,"right":56,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":52,"left":50,"right":51,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":50,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":51,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":56,"left":53,"right":55,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":53,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nucleari